FieldSet.description: CommunicationEndpoint: CMDB Class that stores information about communication protocol endpoints (communication points from which data can be sent or received, linking system or computerinterfaces to logical networks),) that are dedicated to TCP (transmission control protocol) or UDP (user datagram protocol). This class is a combination of the DMTF CIM_ TCPProtocolEndpoint and CIM_UDPProtocolEndpoint classes.
FieldSet.label: Communication Endpoint
